These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
Color: azure, black, chestnut, blood-red
House: townhouse, futuristic, farmhouse, cape-cod
1. House:futuristic is on the left of House:townhouse##1
2. Color:azure == House:cape-cod##1
3. House:farmhouse is on the right of House:townhouse##1
4. Color:black is on the left of House:cape-cod##1
5. Color:blood-red is on the left of House:townhouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Color          | blood-red | chestnut | black | azure   |
| House   | futuristic  | townhouse     | farmhouse   | cape-cod |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
Cigar: tiparillo, game, bluemaster, blend
Food: potato, grapefruit, nectarine, raspberry
1. Cigar:blend == Food:grapefruit##1
2. Cigar:tiparillo is on the far right##1
3. Cigar:game is on the right of Cigar:blend##1
4. Cigar:blend is on the right of Food:nectarine##1
5. Food:grapefruit is on the left of Food:potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Cigar   | bluemaster | blend | game | tiparillo    |
| Food   | nectarine    | grapefruit      | potato | raspberry |

