.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
Transport: boat, jet-ski, bus, quad-bike
Sport: ice-hockey, lacrosse, baseball, snowboarding
1. Sport:baseball is on the left of Sport:snowboarding##1
2. Transport:boat == Sport:ice-hockey##1
3. Sport:lacrosse is on the far right##1
4. Sport:snowboarding is on the right of Transport:quad-bike##1
5. Transport:bus is on the left of Sport:lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Transport         | boat | quad-bike | bus   | jet-ski |
| Sport   | ice-hockey   | baseball | snowboarding | lacrosse         |

